name: Experiment Or Die #8
description: Despite these works being offered up in a purely digital medium, I am an analog type of person at heart. I love grit, and grime, and texture, and I've become quite accustomed to using technology as a means to distort, warp or plain beat up imagery to make it a little bit removed from its original state. Through these methods you end up with things you could never have planned for, and that is exactly what this year long project is about. Staying consistent with making new work, but going into each new day with no plan and no idea what will come next.
